paragraphs.title: Load all countries and all capitals
paragraphs.text:
// Load all countries
val allCountriesDF = spark.read.parquet("data/spatial/countries-poly.parquet").select("name", "shape")
allCountriesDF.registerTempTable("allCountries")
val allCountries = allCountriesDF.map(row => (row.getString(1), row.getString(0)))

// Load all capitals
val capitalsDF = spark.read.parquet("data/spatial/capitals.parquet").select("name", "shape")
capitalsDF.registerTempTable("capitals")
val capitals = capitalsDF.map(row => (row.getString(1), row.getString(0)))

// Define ShapeLuceneRDD
val shapes = ShapeLuceneRDD(allCountries)
shapes.cache
